text: Milovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Milovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2,767 as of 2010. There are 68 streets. == Geography == It is located 13 km from Ufa. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Milovka
